(* §7  MULTIWAY SYSTEM                                              *)
(* The 0x/ tree IS a multiway graph.                               *)
(* Spine = deterministic backbone, checkpoints = branch points     *)
(* iff classifies which branches survive (explorable/collapsed)    *)
(* States graph: all reachable states                              *)
(* Branchial graph: spacelike separation (simultaneous fronts)    *)
(* Causal graph: timelike dependencies between rule applications   *)
(* WolframModel: hypergraph rewriting from the five instructions   *)
(* ================================================================ *)


(* ── Multiway Rewriting Rules ────────────────────────────────── *)
(* Extracted from the 0x unified hypergraph                      *)
(* init = deterministic spine, goto = nondeterministic branch    *)
